@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_lqnfrs(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.cos((wp.sin(v2 + 0.45) * 0.71))
    v1 = (tmp / ((tmp + 0.84 * v2 + 1.00) - (v1 + 0.79 / v0 + 0.78)))
    v0 = (wp.sin((v1 + 0.38 - v2 + 0.19)) - 0.15)
    v2 = ((0.18 + wp.cos(v0 + 0.75)) - v0)
    tmp = wp.abs(wp.abs((v2 + 0.11 * v0 + 0.97)))
    v1 = (tmp * wp.cos(wp.abs(tmp + 0.02)))
    v0 = (wp.cos(wp.exp(v1 + 0.10)) - v2)
    data[tid] = v0
